# Multi-Agent Awareness

- Another tool may continue this work.
- Persist decisions in `TODO.md`, `FIXME.md`, and `WHERE_LEFT_OFF.md`.
- Use the matching working files for the task domain instead of leaving important state only in chat.
- Do not silently overwrite unresolved work from another agent.
- Use the single-writer model.
